益，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/110%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1502%2c20211130%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,110,簡,1502,20211130,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1502","JDATE":"20211130","JTITLE":"竊盜"}